00:07:58.960 --> 00:07:59.640
Sir.

00:07:59.640 --> 00:08:00.120
Mm.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:02.000
Put that down here.

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:04.440
All right.

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.240
My goodness!

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:11.440
Look at all these treasures!

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:13.960
Keep your mouth shut.

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:15.360
You're drooling.

00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:17.240
Am I?

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:19.600
Well, Musheng,

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.960
we owe this

00:08:21.200 --> 00:08:22.200
to you.

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:24.720
A hero deserves a fine sword.

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:30.080
At my age,

00:08:30.320 --> 00:08:31.520
this is all I enjoy.

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:35.160
I'm in a good mood today.

00:08:35.660 --> 00:08:36.680
Come to my place tonight.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:37.980
Let's have some fun.

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.080
Got it, Boss.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.640
I'll bring a few bottles of good wine.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.040
Musheng.

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:45.360
Bring

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:47.800
your Rose too.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:49.400
The more, the merrier.

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:50.000
All right?

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:53.320
What's wrong?

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:54.600
Did you have a lover's spat?

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:56.040
No.

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:58.360
We'll be there.

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:07.520
Rose.

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:12.040
What brings you here?

00:09:12.400 --> 00:09:13.240
Missed me?

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:14.560
Of course.

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:15.800
A day apart

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:17.160
feels like three years.

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:18.720
Smooth talker.

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:37.280
Put this on.

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:39.600
What's this?

00:09:41.880 --> 00:09:42.680
A dress.

00:09:42.900 --> 00:09:43.760
You bought it for me?

00:09:44.520 --> 00:09:45.360
Hurry and change.

00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:46.600
I'm taking you out.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:48.360
Out where?

00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:50.920
Dinner.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:52.840
You're treating me?

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.200
I hope this isn't a trap.

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:06.560
Are you going to watch me get changed?

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:09.480
I suppose I could,

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.680
if you want me to.

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:24.720
How do I look?

00:10:50.680 --> 00:10:51.480
Beautiful.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.240
Zhou Musheng,

00:10:58.560 --> 00:10:59.360
the truth is,

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:03.400
I'm the "Red Bean"
everyone's been looking for.

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:06.520
I knew.

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:08.560
You did?

00:11:09.080 --> 00:11:10.360
I knew the moment

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:12.120
I met you.

00:11:13.400 --> 00:11:14.200
Then, why did you…

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:15.580
I don't care if you're a red bean,

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.400
green bean,

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:17.360
or black bean.

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:19.520
All I know

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:21.280
is

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:23.600
I've fallen hard for you.

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.120
You're the green bean.

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:28.900
Your whole family's green beans.

